{"tid":676710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"幾千天雲加幸福嗎 每日忙碌嗎 仍然是那麼認真嗎？","createTime":"2018-05-24T14:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T08:42:04.000Z","uid":36497,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"95797b8fd9f1a72b589c831ee8e8d253583ea27b","tid":676710,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"幾千天雲加幸福嗎 每日忙碌嗎 仍然是那麼認真嗎？<br />\n可有新球隊 成熟的球隊 成熟到沒再共你吵架<br />\n是阿仙奴拒絕成長嗎 為何沒法裝作瀟灑<br />\n不敗多少年 仍然想當年 仍然幼稚到又記起你 天真夠嗎<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/224612_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F224612_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e1006a68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a6a3e7e0991b26ac988645040cbf55969adb3e5","tid":676710,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9711ddd609ccfe97e0c30e1c84cbd9d48ee6461","tid":676710,"uid":17081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.arsenal.com/sites/default/files/styles/large_16x9/public/gun__1475326918_AW-711-TWR.jpg?itok=2jX5-xn5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arsenal.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge_16x9%2Fpublic%2Fgun__1475326918_AW-711-TWR.jpg%3Fitok%3D2jX5-xn5&h=4a97d61a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90a1e9ba6aa756582d0481b91b2f9e84adb3a0d3","tid":676710,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"個個都講愛美麗 已經無乜人記得雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34898df3405d3